When a Sektor is created, it is created with import restrictions & export requirements.

Restrictions and requirements are set for specific resource types.

Import restriction:
Maximum value of import allowed.
If not specified, restriction is 0 (no import allowed for that resource).

Export requirements:
Minimum value of export required.
If not specified, requirement is 0 (no export required for that resource).

Connected to this, each Sektor has a status.
Initially, a Sektor's status is "Unfinished".
If all requirements are met, and no restrictions are exceeded, a Sektor's status is "Finished".

